  <brief_title>Effect of Local Infiltration Analgesia in Total Hip Arthroplasty</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Local Infiltration Analgesia With Ropivacaine in Total Hip Arthroplasty: a Prospective, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Trail</official_title>
